    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just that they're helping, it's that they have to. i see them making plans for the weekend and then having to cancel because i'm having a bad day or i can't get around. it just feels like my existence is a subtraction from their lives. like, wouldn't things just be lighter for everyone if they didn't have to worry about me anymore?",
